Woman pays heavy price for childlessness Ngede, the chairman of Nyanza Council of Church Leaders, which brings together more than 200 different denominations' heads, was distinguished as a hero on Saturday. He received a certificate of recognition from the Ministry of Sports, Culture and Heritage. On Sunday, faithful of his Power of Jesus Christ Around the World church in Kachok joined him in a thanksgiving mass.